name: Randomness in Puzzles
tagline: lost in the hunt for certainty.
body:
### Welcome to My Work.
This is just a start of something that I've meant to test out this year. I still don't know what it will evolve into since I'm not a real developer (_lame_). Anyways, I learnt that the best way to commit is to test the water first so here I am.

### Contact
I'm the sole author of this __project__, but I will not take responsibility of any disasters coming with my work,  _joking_.
